    </div>

    <p>A properly formulated men's multivitamin gummy should contain zero iron (men accumulate iron; excess causes organ damage), elevated zinc and selenium (testosterone and prostate support), adequate vitamin D3 (42% of Americans are deficient), B vitamins for energy metabolism, and ideally omega-3 DHA/EPA for cardiovascular and cognitive health. The products below are ranked by how effectively they address these male-specific priorities, not just by total nutrient count.</p>

